          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Budgetary Accuracy in Scoring Interest Costs Act of 2019 or the BASIC Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires cost estimates prepared by the Congressional Budget Office or the Joint Committee on Taxation to include the costs of servicing the public debt. </p>]]></text>
